{"n":"game rules ","v":7,"a":[7,48],"p":[{"b":132,"t":2,"a":[12,37,36],"e":"RULES:
DESTROY THE INCOMING ASTROIDS TO SURVIVE.

ACTIVATE THE CANNONS USING THE TRIANGLE BUTTONS.  FIRE THE 
CANNONS PRESSING THE GREEN OR RED CIRCLE BUTTONS ONCE ACTIVATED.
NOTE, RED AND GREEN CAN NOT BE ACTIVE AT THE SAME TIME.
USE THE YELLOW BUTTON WHEN THINGS GET TOUGH.  THIS WILL
FIRE ALL THE HEALTHY CANNONS.  THIS HAS A 20 SECOND COOLDOWN.

YOU'LL NEED TO REPAIR THE CANNONS TO KEEP THEIR HEALTH UNDER
100 USING THE DIAMOND BUTTONS TO YOUR LEFT AND RIGHT.  THESE BUTTONS
CAN ALSO BE SHOT AT TO PRESS THEM, IF YOU CAN'T REACH.  CANNONS THAT 
ARE 100 OR OVER WILL BECOME UNUSABLE UNTIL REPAIRED. THEY WILL ALSO
CATCH FIRE!

THE NEXT TIME AN UNUSEABLE CANNON TAKES DAMAGE, IT WILL 
DAMAGE THE SHIPS MAIN HEALTH, SHOWN BY THE YELLOW NUMBER ABOVE.

REACHING 2000 WILL CAUSE YOU TO LOSE!

HOW LONG CAN YOU SURVIVE?  BE SURE TO LOG YOUR HIGH SCORES ON THE 
BOARD ON YOUR LEFT.  ALSO, CHECK OUT THE QUESTS!","s":[{"p":[0,0,0],"r":[0,0,0],"s":[0.001983933,0.001982265,0.001983703],"c":[0,0.6666667,0.1523809],"b":["when told by any  gamerules then become next in 0.7s","when starts then turn invisible"]},{"p":[0,0,0],"r":[0,0,0],"s":[0.001983933,0.001982265,0.001983703],"c":[0,0.6666667,0.1523809],"b":["when starts then turn visible","when told by any  gamerules then become previous in 0s"]}]}]}
